SOCIETY OF CINCINNATI.</HEAD>
<P>VOTED, That Mr. BEERS and Mr. PINTO wait on the Reverend Doctor DWIGHT, with the Thanks of this Society for his Sermon delivered before them this Day, and reque&s;t a Copy of the &s;ame for Publication, at the Expen&s;e of the Society.</P>
